 Multiply Equation 2 with ($0.3236+\imath0.7316$)
  \begin{equation}
   (0.3236+\imath0.7316).x_1 + 0.64x_2 = 0
 \end{equation}
  \begin{equation}
   (0.3236+\imath0.7316).x_1 - (0.64).x_2 = 0
 \end{equation}
 Equation 1 - Equation 2\\
   \[1.28.x_2 = 0\]
   \[ x_2 = 0\]
 Subsituting $x_2$ in Equation 1, we get\\
   \[ x_1 = 0 \]
